Class SequenceDataController

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ControlPositionSequenceDataController

    public class SequenceDataController
extends TypeController
    A TypeController for sequence data.

    If stored data are wanted, it will first request the first and last sequence number for the appropriate data type and within the specified from/to time stamps. It will then, repeatedly, request stored data until it has them all.

    If live data is disconnected and then reconnected, it will make sure to make a request for the sequence number interval that have been missed.

    Author:
    Jan Marthedal Rasmussen
